BEGIN:VCALENDAR
VERSION:2.0
PRODID:-//Thiccctionary//Roadmap Reminders//EN
CALSCALE:GREGORIAN
METHOD:PUBLISH
X-WR-CALNAME:Thiccctionary — Book Roadmap
X-WR-CALDESC:Recurring reminders for Phase 1 (catalog hardening) → April 2027 launch.
X-WR-TIMEZONE:America/Denver

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:thiccctionary-weekly-curation-2026
SUMMARY:Thiccctionary — Weekly curation pass
DESCRIPTION:Open Claude (Cowork). Say "let's curate this week." Claude lists the 7 most recent entries; for each\, you reply book or web. ~10 minutes total. Marks each entry's bookReady flag for the eventual book.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Denver:20260510T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Denver:20260510T101500
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=SU
LOCATION:thiccctionary.com
URL:https://thiccctionary.com/archive.html
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Curate the past week's entries
TRIGGER:-PT0M
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:thiccctionary-monthly-status-2026
SUMMARY:Thiccctionary — Monthly book-status check
DESCRIPTION:Open Claude. Ask "where are we on the book?" Claude reads the roadmap memory and reports current phase\, catalog size\, next decision-point. ~5 minutes. Recalibrate if drifting.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Denver:20260601T093000
DTEND;TZID=America/Denver:20260601T094000
RRULE:FREQ=MONTHLY;BYMONTHDAY=1
LOCATION:thiccctionary.com
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Book roadmap status check
TRIGGER:-PT0M
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:thiccctionary-quarterly-recalibration-2026
SUMMARY:Thiccctionary — Quarterly recalibration
DESCRIPTION:Open Claude. Major review — should we accelerate\, slow down\, or kill the plan? Look at audience growth\, catalog quality\, time available. ~30 minutes.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Denver:20260801T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Denver:20260801T103000
RRULE:FREQ=MONTHLY;INTERVAL=3;BYMONTHDAY=1
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Quarterly recalibration
TRIGGER:-PT0M
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:thiccctionary-phase2-decision-2026
SUMMARY:Thiccctionary — Phase 2 begins (POD partner decision)
DESCRIPTION:Decide: KDP (Amazon\, low fees) vs IngramSpark (bookstore distribution\, more fees) vs Blurb (premium quality\, expensive POD). Block 2 hours. Claude has the comparison ready.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Denver:20260706T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Denver:20260706T120000
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Choose POD partner
TRIGGER:-P1D
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:thiccctionary-phase3-decision-2026
SUMMARY:Thiccctionary — Phase 3 begins (layout tool decision)
DESCRIPTION:Decide layout tool. Affinity Publisher (cheap\, professional)\, InDesign (industry standard\, subscription)\, or LaTeX (free\, code-driven). Build the entries.json → PDF pipeline.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Denver:20261005T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Denver:20261005T120000
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Choose layout tool
TRIGGER:-P1D
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:thiccctionary-phase4-final-curation-2026
SUMMARY:Thiccctionary — Phase 4 begins (final curation + foreword)
DESCRIPTION:Pick the ~250 best entries for Vol. I. Write the foreword (~1500-2000 words). Draft print-exclusive content. ~40-60 hours over 4 months.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Denver:20261201T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Denver:20261201T103000
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Final curation + foreword sprint
TRIGGER:-P3D
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:thiccctionary-preorder-launch-2027
SUMMARY:Thiccctionary — Pre-orders open
DESCRIPTION:Pre-order page goes live ~6 weeks before fulfillment. Press kit ready. Influencer outreach campaign begins.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Denver:20270301T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Denver:20270301T103000
BEGIN:VALARM
